### rpiv-ask-user-question (rpiv-mono)

https://github.com/juicesharp/rpiv-mono

The built-in `ask_user_question` tool in this package is adapted from the
rpiv-ask-user-question package. The schema design and UX pattern are derived
from that work. Install `@juicesharp/rpiv-ask-user-question` for the full
implementation with tabbed TUI, previews, and localization.

